videos.description: Norfolk State's Steven Whitley picks the pocket of  North Carolina Central's Larry McKnight Jr., and C.J. Kelley finishes at the rim with a lay-in.
videos.headline: Whitley steals, Kelly scores

videos.description: Norfolk State's Armani Branch threads the needle with a beautiful bounce pass to Alex Long, who throws down the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Branch delivers nice pass for Long's dunk

videos.description: North Carolina Central's Raasean Davis misses a contested jumper, but he runs in to throw down the thunderous two-handed putback dunk.
videos.headline: Davis hammers emphatic putback dunk

videos.description: Norfolk State's Mastadi Pitt miss the game-tying three, which secures a third straight MEAC title for North Carolina Central.
videos.headline: North Carolina Central wins MEAC and NCAA tourney bid
